      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;what&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;What? &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#what&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Good question.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m hoping to write down some of my thoughts on computers as I white-knuckle it into the future.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Recently I&amp;rsquo;ve been interested in the following:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Distributed Systems&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Linux, Nix, et al.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Endurance/Strength Training&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;terminus&#34; class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Terminus &lt;span class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34; style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#terminus&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shout out to &lt;a href=&#34;https://eyalkalderon.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Eyal Kalderon&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/getzola/zola?tab=readme-ov-file&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noreferrer&#34;&gt;Zola&lt;/a&gt; website theme.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
